⟨hot er dem⟩, iz geven a gantse biblyotek; mayn tate hot gehat a gantse biblyotek.

00:12:04.229 --> 00:12:09.161
di, dos yidishkeyt v- hobn mir ge- di meydlekh gelernt, der t- der tate hot undz oysgelernt.

00:12:09.298 --> 00:12:10.932
UNK, ikh lez

00:12:10.932 --> 00:12:14.769
⟨ot der,⟩ dem a-... UNK azoy heyst er? "Der Heymatland". ales lez ikh iber,

00:12:14.769 --> 00:12:16.987
un lez un shrayb yidish.

00:12:17.027 --> 00:12:18.095
un dos ales

00:12:18.095 --> 00:12:19.889
a dank mayn tate.

00:12:20.250 --> 00:12:27.669
ikh bin geven ⟨in⟩ dray un akhtsikstn yor, bin ikh geven in ISRAEL mit mayn man, mit der yingerer tokhter, iz nokh nisht geven khasene gehat.

00:12:28.063 --> 00:12:30.641
⟨un⟩ dortn hot men gehert az ikh bin gekumen,

00:12:30.641 --> 00:12:33.188
zenen ongekumen fun ale, fun, fun,

00:12:33.188 --> 00:12:37.438
fun ale shtetlekh dortn vu zey voynen, fleg men ku- iz men gekumen mikh zen,

00:12:37.438 --> 00:12:38.844
un m'hot yeder gebrakht

00:12:38.844 --> 00:12:40.587
gelt; ikh bin nor vos gekumen.

00:12:40.587 --> 00:12:44.257
zog ikh, "ikh da- ikh kum nisht aher..." i- ikh hob ongebrakht mit mayn m⟨an s-⟩

00:12:44.257 --> 00:12:46.148
a sakh, GESCHENKE dortn,

00:12:46.148 --> 00:12:48.239
zakhn; er hot do teykef gearbet...

00:12:48.803 --> 00:12:51.902
"darf, ikh darf nisht keyn nedoves," zog ikh, "ikh darf nisht hobn."

00:12:51.992 --> 00:12:56.913
 zogt er, "neyn, undz ze'mir shuldik aykh!" "vos ⟨bist⟩, vos shuldik, ver sh-...?"

00:12:56.937 --> 00:12:59.940
"dos vos undz ken'mir," zogt er, "vos undz ken'mir,

00:12:59.940 --> 00:13:01.549
dos d- a dank dayn tate.

00:13:01.549 --> 00:13:03.781
un undz ze'mir shuldik zeyer a sakh.

00:13:03.889 --> 00:13:07.022
az ikh ke- undz ken'mir nisht dem tatn opgibn, vel'mir dir gibn."

00:13:07.635 --> 00:13:12.516
zogt mir, in vosere RELIGIOZe, vos far a religye iz gevezn? velkhe,

00:13:12.516 --> 00:13:15.974
in velkhe shuln zayt ir gegangen, b⟨ote⟩-medroshim, ⟨oder⟩,

00:13:15.685 --> 00:13:16.770
 ikh bin ge-...

00:13:15.974 --> 00:13:17.113
ayer mishpokhe?

00:13:16.770 --> 00:13:19.256
ikh bin gegang-... di mishpokhe oder ikh?

00:13:18.908 --> 00:13:20.539
ayer mishpokhe, ir oykh.

00:13:19.684 --> 00:13:20.876
UNK.

00:13:21.034 --> 00:13:27.152
mayn, funem tatn, UNK, di mame veyst ir oykhet, un mayn m-, mame's brider,

00:13:27.152 --> 00:13:29.923
zey zenen geboyrn, zenen geven,

00:13:29.923 --> 00:13:33.363
 zeyer yung funem tatn, geblibn.

00:13:33.488 --> 00:13:38.573
nor zey hobn zikh, di muter... zey hobn gehat oykh felder, velder... fleg alts farkoyfn a shtik feld

00:13:38.573 --> 00:13:42.236
un gibn... zey hobn shtark gesht- -shtrebt tsu, di kinder zoln lernen,

00:13:42.236 --> 00:13:45.457
vayl zey zenen geven z- ofene kep; zey hobn azoy gut gelernt.

00:13:45.457 --> 00:13:48.264
un zi hot gevolt, s'zol, s'zol kumen tsu epes.

00:13:48.473 --> 00:13:50.714
hobn zey gelernt in Tshernevits,

00:13:50.714 --> 00:13:52.719
funem dorf keyn Tshernevits,

00:13:52.827 --> 00:13:56.021
un zey hobn geendikt dortn dos GYMNASIUM,

00:13:56.021 --> 00:13:59.118
un zenen gegangen keyn Vin, keyn Vin.

00:13:59.118 --> 00:14:01.798
dortn hobn zey geendikt di univerzitet,

00:14:01.804 --> 00:14:02.928
in Vin,

00:14:03.053 --> 00:14:05.055
un zenen gevorn groyse mentshn.

00:14:05.162 --> 00:14:11.923
der, elterer bruder, Fayvl, er iz gevorn a advokat, yurist.

00:14:12.064 --> 00:14:16.929
un do hot er nokh gepraktitsirt UNK ⟨s'iz⟩ geven farbunen Tshernevits mit Vin,

00:14:16.929 --> 00:14:21.609
un er hot geendikt oyf a, der best- der bester shiler fun der univerzitet.

00:14:21.632 --> 00:14:26.092
hot ⟨men im⟩ durkhgefirt in, in sht-..., mayn man hot, mame hot dertseylt...

00:14:26.092 --> 00:14:30.020
m'hot im durkhgefirt dortn oyf a ⟨koles-WAGEN⟩... ir veyst vos heyst a ⟨koles-WAGEN⟩?

00:14:30.020 --> 00:14:30.925
fyaker...

00:14:31.032 --> 00:14:32.340
iber der shtot,

00:14:32.340 --> 00:14:34.957
un er hot gek- -krigt a ring fun der univerzitet

00:14:34.957 --> 00:14:36.375
mit a brilyant,

00:14:36.499 --> 00:14:38.855
der advokat, der Fayvl.

00:14:39.756 --> 00:14:42.956
der tsveyter bruder, Volf...

00:14:42.844 --> 00:14:44.643
dos iz ayer onkl?

00:14:43.620 --> 00:14:46.882
⟨a- ⟩, dos iz mayn m- mame's

00:14:44.785 --> 00:14:46.298
ayer a feter?

00:14:46.882 --> 00:14:48.069
briders.

00:14:48.767 --> 00:14:51.309
dos iz geven der ershter onkl, Fayvl.

00:14:51.805 --> 00:14:53.556
⟨ot⟩ der tsveyter onkl,

00:14:53.556 --> 00:14:58.568
 iz ⟨d-⟩ gevorn a... ⟨vi⟩ heyst es? in ershtn velt-krig hot men im ayngerufn tsu,

00:14:58.568 --> 00:15:02.412
 tsu d⟨er⟩ militer, ⟨R-⟩, ÖSTERREICH-UNGARN.

00:15:02.520 --> 00:15:07.188
iz er gefaln in plen, in, in gefangenshaft tsu di rusn.

00:15:07.870 --> 00:15:14.202
un b- dortn in gefangenshaft, hot zikh bay im oysgeartet dos KOMMUNI-, KOMMUNISMUS un azoy vayter.

00:15:14.202 --> 00:15:17.660
hot er ongehoybn sh-, ⟨DIESE⟩, ⟨tsu⟩,

00:15:17.660 --> 00:15:21.177
shoyn tsu geyn mit der revolutsye, ⟨iz er⟩ aroys mit der revolutsye.

00:15:21.218 --> 00:15:25.889
biz vanet er iz gevorn a, er hot geendikt di k- akademye

00:15:25.889 --> 00:15:28.501
FRU- IMENI FRUNZE in MOSCOW

00:15:28.592 --> 00:15:30.661
un iz gevorn a groyser general.

00:15:31.123 --> 00:15:34.414
hot er gekemft vu ir vilt: in Finland, un,

00:15:34.414 --> 00:15:37.563
un s'letste mol iz er geven in Shpanyen,

00:15:37.570 --> 00:15:42.579
un dortn, shteyt geshribn, er hot geretet di, di shtot Madrid,

00:15:42.579 --> 00:15:44.079
un gevorn ⟨a⟩ GEROY,

00:15:44.079 --> 00:15:45.340
un iz aheymgekumen

00:15:45.340 --> 00:15:46.795
zeyer UNK,

00:15:46.795 --> 00:15:50.318
 groyser mentsh un me, fun im hot geshribn,

00:15:50.318 --> 00:15:53.113
iberal shteyt geshribn, ikh hob dortn azoyne bikher.

00:15:53.113 --> 00:15:56.751
di gantse velt iz geven mit zayn, bild, mit zayn,

00:15:56.824 --> 00:15:58.500
 ver er iz.

00:15:58.500 --> 00:16:01.408
d- do in Amerike iz er geven in di draysikste yorn.

00:16:01.414 --> 00:16:06.166
hot er g- hot men geshribn, un m'hot undz geshikt tsaytungen nokh ahin, keyn Rumenyen.

00:16:06.308 --> 00:16:10.132
hot men undz geshikt, hot men gezogt az er

00:16:10.206 --> 00:16:13.274
iz a m- mentsh fun der legende,

00:16:13.274 --> 00:16:16.261
un hot men bashribn fun vanet er shtamt: "fun a

00:16:16.261 --> 00:16:18.486
oremer yidisher familye,

00:16:18.576 --> 00:16:20.679
un er hot UNK azoy vayt gebrakht."

00:16:20.770 --> 00:16:24.712
un, un iz gekumen aheym fun Shpanyen,

00:16:25.090 --> 00:16:26.788
mit AUSZEICHNUNG,

00:16:26.878 --> 00:16:28.745
UNK vi a general

00:16:28.954 --> 00:16:31.580
un ales, a held fun Shpanyen.

00:16:31.857 --> 00:16:34.386
un dortn hot men teykef gegibn a nem

00:16:34.386 --> 00:16:36.170
un arayngevorfn in der tfise.

00:16:36.852 --> 00:16:40.746
ale GENERÄLE, s'iz geven dokh oyf di GENERÄLE, hot men i- iz er oykh arayngefaln.

00:16:40.746 --> 00:16:44.000
er iz shoyn nisht aroysgekumen fun dem, fun der tfise.

00:16:43.585 --> 00:16:48.965
ver, zogt mir, ver zaynen nokh gevezn fun ayer mishpokhe, ⟨d- VOT, f-⟩...?

00:16:47.618 --> 00:16:51.049
dos iz der tsveyter, un der driter iz geven,

00:16:51.049 --> 00:16:52.303
 Volf.

00:16:53.271 --> 00:16:56.389
er iz geven oykh a general, fun GEHEIME,

00:16:56.389 --> 00:16:57.551
sekretne.

00:16:58.384 --> 00:17:02.242
un er, er hot zeyer a sakh oyfgetun, zeyer a sakh.

00:17:02.242 --> 00:17:04.046
zey hobn gekemft GEGEN FASCHISMUS.

00:17:04.046 --> 00:17:05.921
zey f- zey flegn aroysgeyn

00:17:06.028 --> 00:17:10.945
in front, flegn zey aroysgeyn, un shrayen tsu di day-... vayl zey hobn gekent zeyer gut daytsh...

00:17:10.945 --> 00:17:13.315
hobn ⟨g-⟩ flegn zey shrayen tsu di daytshn,

00:17:13.315 --> 00:17:15.286
⟨,⟩ "⟨GEBT EUCH UNTER⟩.

00:17:15.292 --> 00:17:18.070
⟨DAS KÄMPFEN IST UMSONST⟩.

00:17:18.070 --> 00:17:19.890
⟨DER KRIEG IST VERLOREN⟩.

00:17:19.890 --> 00:17:24.022
 GE-, un ⟨WIR, WIR SCH- SCHENKEN DAS LEBEN UN GARANTIEREN EUCH⟩."

00:17:24.022 --> 00:17:27.420
flegn zey azoy zikh lo-, lozn in plen.

00:17:27.713 --> 00:17:30.554
ale flegn zikh ibergibn in,

00:17:30.554 --> 00:17:31.773
in gefangenshaft:

00:17:31.773 --> 00:17:34.712
gantse, gantse kompanyes flegn geyn

00:17:34.712 --> 00:17:36.687
⟨az⟩ di Shterns flegn aroysgeyn

00:17:36.687 --> 00:17:38.135
un redn in dem,

00:17:38.732 --> 00:17:43.518
nu, in dem, di groyse TAR- vi azoy heyst dos? di, ot o, in dem,

00:17:43.390 --> 00:17:44.852
⟨ir meynt⟩ di radyo?

00:17:43.828 --> 00:17:46.246
in gramofon, in dem gramofon.

00:17:46.246 --> 00:17:52.718
 un, flegn zikh, gezogt, di, di, di OFITSERSTVO mit di komandirn, flegn zey redn oyf daytsh,

00:17:52.718 --> 00:17:54.082
"git zikh unter!

00:17:54.223 --> 00:17:55.904
der krig iz farloyrn."

00:17:56.468 --> 00:18:02.578
zogt mir, mir'n zikh kern a bisl tsurik, tsu der tsayt ven ir hot gelebt tsuzamen mit ayer mishpokhe,

00:18:02.578 --> 00:18:04.528
vegn dem religyezn lebn.

00:18:03.943 --> 00:18:04.477
a.

00:18:05.496 --> 00:18:13.584
dortn iz geven shtark a frum shtetl. zey flegn ale⟨s tsu, ⟩, di ale, vi me zogt, yontoyvim

00:18:13.584 --> 00:18:16.242
h- erlekh haltn. shabes iz geven,

00:18:16.242 --> 00:18:19.631
m'hot nisht gearbet, gornisht. me fleg arumshpatsirn,

00:18:20.375 --> 00:18:22.171
 un me fleg,

00:18:22.171 --> 00:18:25.031
 zikh tsuzamenkumen, di mishpokhe: aher, ahin.

00:18:25.398 --> 00:18:26.724
⟨YA NE ZNAYU⟩ UNK.

00:18:26.809 --> 00:18:28.136
UNK

00:18:27.703 --> 00:18:31.226
 UNK dertseylt... ⟨, y- ⟩.

00:18:28.868 --> 00:18:31.461
⟨nu⟩, vayl, vayl ⟨d-⟩ darf men araynlozn.

00:18:31.226 --> 00:18:31.967
yo.

00:18:32.715 --> 00:18:34.244
iz vos fleg dortn zayn?

00:18:36.715 --> 00:18:41.332
 UNK, mir flegn haltn dortn mish- di shabes haltn un...

00:18:41.592 --> 00:18:46.148
i- ir gedenkt yidishe yontoyvim fleg⟨n- -t ir⟩ UNK?

00:18:41.642 --> 00:18:43.104
un,...

00:18:44.764 --> 00:18:47.072
o, ya! fleg ⟨gey-⟩...

00:18:46.148 --> 00:18:48.589
ir kent dertseyln, gedenkt velkhe fun zey?

00:18:47.072 --> 00:18:48.287
yo.

00:18:48.287 --> 00:18:53.046
me fleg geyn tsu simkhes-toyres mit a fondele. mir fleg'mir di kinder bay der toyre,

00:18:53.046 --> 00:18:55.797
fleg men kleyne toyres, fleg men gibn di kinder in di hent.

00:18:55.797 --> 00:19:00.615
un me fleg, zingen un tantsn. ⟨do- es⟩ iz geven der shenster yontev,

00:19:00.615 --> 00:19:01.413
..

00:19:02.852 --> 00:19:05.668
der shenster yontev iz geven,

00:19:05.668 --> 00:19:07.066
simkhes-toyre.

00:19:07.275 --> 00:19:10.171
velkhe yontoyvim hot ir mer, ammerstn lib gehat?

00:19:07.461 --> 00:19:08.379
nu...

00:19:10.506 --> 00:19:11.664
peysekh.

00:19:12.540 --> 00:19:14.865
ir gedenkt, vi fleg bay aykh forkumen

00:19:14.802 --> 00:19:16.224
dem peysekh?

00:19:15.324 --> 00:19:16.916
der seyder? ye.

00:19:16.224 --> 00:19:17.648
o, ya! d-...

00:19:16.916 --> 00:19:18.542
kent ir dertseyln epes?

00:19:17.648 --> 00:19:23.333
UNK seyder bay undz iz ge- di brider arum un arum. s'iz geven, keyn eyn-hore, a sheyner tish, UNK

00:19:23.333 --> 00:19:26.518
zeks kinder, un di babe, un di eltern.

00:19:26.518 --> 00:19:29.580
un me fleg zeyer sheyn, der tate fleg praven a seyder az,

00:19:29.580 --> 00:19:30.990
⟨hot⟩ gemegt geyn tsun im

00:19:30.990 --> 00:19:31.952
hern nor.

00:19:31.952 --> 00:19:33.731
⟨un,⟩ me fleg,

00:19:33.731 --> 00:19:37.647
di brider flegn, fregn di fir kashes un,

00:19:37.647 --> 00:19:40.499
un se fleg zikh praven biz shpet in der nakht.

00:19:40.499 --> 00:19:43.688
me fleg esn, gibn latkes mit

00:19:43.688 --> 00:19:46.655
ales. s'iz geven zeyer, zeyer, zeyer, sheyn.

00:19:46.864 --> 00:19:48.933
in vos far a shul hot ir zikh gelernt?

00:19:49.024 --> 00:19:52.535
ikh hob mikh gelernt in der rumenisher shul, in der folks-shul,

00:19:52.602 --> 00:19:54.570
hob gemakht akht klasn.

00:19:54.694 --> 00:19:57.894
kh'hob mikh gelernt in der daytsher shul; ikh hob gemakht fir klasn.

00:19:58.052 --> 00:20:02.045
dernokh dem bin ikh gegangen un ikh hob gelernt, der tate hot undz gelernt yidish.

00:20:02.136 --> 00:20:05.406
⟨gemuzt⟩ kenen, diktant fleg ikh shraybn,

00:20:05.406 --> 00:20:07.204
diktirn. dernokh dem fleg er,

00:20:07.204 --> 00:20:09.389
 durkhkukn tsi s'iz gut.

00:20:09.389 --> 00:20:11.707
un ⟨s'i- fe-⟩ er fleg haltn shtreng⟨s⟩.

00:20:11.707 --> 00:20:14.578
er iz densmolt nisht geven keyn tatn; er iz geven a lerer.

00:20:14.578 --> 00:20:15.611
er hot gezogt,

00:20:15.611 --> 00:20:17.536
"ikh bin mer keyn tate nisht itster;

00:20:17.536 --> 00:20:20.388
ikh bin itster a lerer. ir muzst kenen."

00:20:20.563 --> 00:20:22.970
un bay im ho'mir gelernt yidishkeyt.

00:20:23.145 --> 00:20:28.420
ah, ales: di brokhes, UNK, ale brokhes un leyenen un krishme un,

00:20:28.420 --> 00:20:31.579
un, un moyde-ani. ales ho'mir gedarft kenen.

00:20:31.579 --> 00:20:35.604
tsu yeder zakh hot men gedarft kenen a brokhe: m'iz gegangen tsum broyt, a brokhe.

00:20:35.604 --> 00:20:39.449
oystrinken vayn, di, hot men gedarft oykh hagofn makhn.

00:20:39.449 --> 00:20:42.309
tsu yeder, afile az s'iz geven a duner in droysn,

00:20:42.636 --> 00:20:46.173
un s'iz geven a blits, ho'mir oykh gedarft visn a, a brokhe.

00:20:47.074 --> 00:20:49.130
un,...

00:20:49.470 --> 00:20:52.862
geven a frum shtetl. dortn iz geven,

00:20:52.862 --> 00:20:54.445
tsienistish; me fleg

00:20:54.445 --> 00:20:57.311
helfn far, far ISRAEL zeyer a sakh.

00:20:57.688 --> 00:21:00.078
un, ⟨,⟩ s'iz geven a sh-...

00:20:59.207 --> 00:21:02.880
a s- a sakh yidishe mishpokhes zaynen gevezn in ayer shtetl?

00:21:02.953 --> 00:21:05.586
s'iz geven CIRCA a dray hundert,

00:21:05.586 --> 00:21:08.823
a dray hundert mentshn..., FAMILIEN, FAMILIEN.

00:21:07.830 --> 00:21:08.819
familye...

00:21:08.823 --> 00:21:11.261
yede familye iz nisht vintsiker geven fun,

00:21:11.261 --> 00:21:12.737
fun akht mentshn,

00:21:12.737 --> 00:21:14.147
in ALLGEMEIN.

00:21:14.147 --> 00:21:16.245
UNK ergets andersh iz geven mer.

00:21:16.673 --> 00:21:20.833
s'iz geven dortn a, a shtetl, vos, in dem shtetl iz geven a familye

00:21:20.833 --> 00:21:22.472
⟨vos hot⟩ gehat fertsn kinder.

00:21:22.883 --> 00:21:26.820
vi zaynen geven ayere batsiungen tsvishn di yidishe familyes

00:21:26.820 --> 00:21:29.101
un andere familyes? ve- v-

00:21:29.101 --> 00:21:32.748
velkhe f- velkhe natsyonalitetn hobn nokh gelebt dortn?

00:21:33.075 --> 00:21:37.220
in dem shtetl hot gelebt zeyer a sakh farshidene natsyonalitetn.

00:21:37.210 --> 00:21:38.368
tsum bayshpil?

00:21:37.294 --> 00:21:41.574
s'hot gelebt, p-, po- poylishe mentshn, FAMILIEN.

00:21:41.682 --> 00:21:43.920
poylishe, tshekhishe,

00:21:43.920 --> 00:21:45.999
daytshe zenen geven zeyer a sakh. s'iz geven

00:21:45.999 --> 00:21:49.269
SOGAR a, a y- a daytshe gase iz geven.

00:21:49.967 --> 00:21:53.651
 daytshn, Ukrayner,

00:21:53.651 --> 00:21:56.435
s'iz geven oykhet afile funem ershtn krig,

00:21:56.435 --> 00:21:59.012
⟨zenen⟩ UNK flegn zayn kozakn vos m'hot ge-

00:21:59.012 --> 00:22:00.565
inem ershtn krig hot men UNK,

00:22:00.565 --> 00:22:02.595
zenen zey ibergeblibn dortn voynen.

00:22:02.595 --> 00:22:04.828
m'hot zey gerufn... vi azoy hot men zey gerufn?

00:22:04.986 --> 00:22:07.598
⟨⟩, fargesn.... nor s'iz geven oykhet

00:22:07.598 --> 00:22:08.979
rusn geven,

00:22:09.306 --> 00:22:11.041
fun di kozakn geblibn.

00:22:11.041 --> 00:22:12.776
